high_descs: Go straight and walk around the coffeetable.
Pick up the apple from the table.
Turn back towards the kitchen area where you started and go to the pan.
Place the apple onto a pan in the fridge.
Remove the pan with the apple on it from the fridge.
Turn left towards the countertop.
Place the pan with the apple on the countertop next to the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place an apple on a pan on the kitchen countertop.

high_descs: Go to the coffeetable and place yourself between the coffeetable and the sofa.
Take the apple.
Go to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator door, place the apple on the pan on the second level.
Take the pan where the apple is located. Close the door.
Move to your back and then position yourself parallel to the countertop.
Place the pan with the apple, after the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Find an apple, find a pan and place them next to the countertop.

high_descs: Go straight to the coffeetable and walk round the coffeetable.
Pick the apple from the table.
Turn right and again walk round the pan, then head to the cupboard.
Place the apple in the cupboard upon the pan by opening the cupboard.
Now pick the pan and the apple from the cupboard, then close it.
Move slightly to the left near the countertop.
Place both the pan and the apple on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: To place both the pan and the apple on the countertop.
